Package org.e2immu.support

Class Lazy<T>

java.lang.Object
org.e2immu.support.Lazy<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the container's content type
public class Lazy<T> extends Object
Implementation of a lazy value, where null is used to indicate that the value has not been evaluated yet.

Currently there is no means of detecting the @Mark annotation, which is why we have added it as a contract.

This is an example class! Please extend and modify for your needs.
